#: /home/carloratm/progetti/postgresql-source/doc-9.0.4/installation.xml:12(para)
msgid "This chapter describes the installation of <productname>PostgreSQL</productname> using the source code distribution. (If you are installing a pre-packaged distribution, such as an RPM or Debian package, ignore this chapter and read the packager's instructions instead.)"
msgstr ""

